### 로그인 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 회원탈퇴
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/me/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "type": "SCHEDULE_INCONVENIENT"
}

### 회원탈퇴 (기타 사유)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/me/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "type": "ETC",
  "description": "기타 사유"
}

### 캐릭터 변경
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/members/me/character/STUDYER
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 새로운 소셜 계정 연동
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/me/social-accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "socialProvider": "NAVER",
  "socialId": "new-social-id"
}

### 소셜 계정 연동 해제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/members/me/social-accounts/NAVER
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
